data.description: Welcome home to this stunning property in the highly sought-after Jack Britt School District! Conveniently located in close proximity to Fort Liberty and shopping areas. Boasting sleek finishes and a thoughtful open-concept plan, this 5 bed, 4.5 bath home is the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. As you enter the home, you will find a large foyer and a study with French doors, as well as a spacious kitchen that includes an oversized pantry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, large island, and separate dining room and eat-in area. Also on the main level is the Master Bedroom w/separate sitting area, walk-in closet, double vanities, soaking tub, and shower. There is also a ½ bath on the main level for guests. Upstairs are 4 additional bedrooms, 2 of which have en-suite full-size baths, with a banister that overlooks the first-floor. Yard is fully irrigated w/extended covered back patio to enjoy larger gatherings. Come and visit this beautiful property before it’s gone!
